title: Couple With Heart Person Person Dark Skin Tone Medium Skin Tone
alsoKnownAs: Couple with heart (person, person, dark skin tone, medium skin tone)
description: Represents a romantic couple, both identified as women, with a dark skin tone and a medium skin tone. It signifies love, partnership, and commitment between two women.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, this emoji portrays a loving couple with distinct skin tones, emphasizing inclusivity and diversity in relationships. The two figures are rendered with Apple's characteristic soft, rounded edges and warm, natural lighting, showcasing a gentle embrace. A heart, glowing with a soft pink hue and subtle 3D highlights, floats between them, symbolizing deep affection, commitment, and unity in romantic partnerships.
